## 5. Search/Discovery Analysis

### Query Terms That Work Well

| Query | Result |
|-------|--------|
| `["imessage"]` | ‚úÖ Returns all 5 iMessage tools |
| `["slack"]` | ‚úÖ Returns all 5 Slack tools |
| `["calendar", "events"]` | ‚úÖ Returns get_events, create_event, delete_event |
| `["gmail", "search"]` | ‚úÖ Returns search_gmail_messages |
| `["unread", "messages"]` | ‚úÖ Returns get_unread from iMessage |
| `["drive", "search", "files"]` | ‚úÖ Returns search_drive_files |
| `["send", "message"]` | ‚úÖ Returns tools from Gmail, iMessage, Google Chat |

### Query Terms That Fail or Return Unexpected Results

| Query | Expected | Actual |
|-------|----------|--------|
| `["notion", "search"]` | Notion tools | ‚ùå Only workspace-mcp/imessage tools (server missing) |
| `["figma", "file"]` | Figma tools | ‚ùå Only Drive tools (server missing) |
| `["supabase", "query"]` | Supabase tools | ‚ùå Unrelated tools (server missing) |
| `["gmail", "search", "email"]` | search_gmail_messages first | ‚ö†Ô∏è find_and_replace_doc ranked first |

### Server Name Matching

| Query | Works? | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| "imessage" | ‚úÖ Yes | Returns iMessage tools |
| "slack" | ‚úÖ Yes | Returns Slack tools |
| "notion" | ‚ùå No | Server not visible |
| "figma" | ‚ùå No | Server not visible |
| "supabase" | ‚ùå No | Server not visible |
| "gmail" | ‚ö†Ô∏è Partial | Works but "workspace-mcp" would be more precise |

